---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Academia Europa · European Professional Education Institution"
  description="Structured postgraduate education for experienced professionals. Charcoal-and-bronze institutional home for Veterinary Academy International and future specialist faculties."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="border-b border-divider" style="background-color: var(--color-charcoal-deep);">
    <div class="container-prose py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="eyebrow mb-6" style="color: var(--color-steel);">European Professional Education</div>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-cream text-5xl md:text-7xl leading-[1.02] max-w-5xl">
        Where Professionals Become Authorities.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-8 max-w-[600px] text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-cream-dim">
        Academia Europa develops structured postgraduate education for experienced professionals across specialised fields, building the kind of deep, documented mastery that defines genuine clinical and professional authority.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/academies" class="btn btn-primary">Explore Our Academies</a>
        <a href="/partnerships" class="btn">Academic Partnerships</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Approach — bookcase background -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <img
      src="/library-shelves.jpg"
      alt=""
      aria-hidden="true"
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
      style="object-position: center center; filter: saturate(0.87);"
      loading="lazy"
      decoding="async"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-color: rgba(28, 26, 23, 0.6);"></div>
    <div class="relative container-prose" style="padding-top: 120px; padding-bottom: 120px;">
      <div class="max-w-5xl">
        <div class="eyebrow mb-3">Our Approach</div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-cream text-3xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.1]" style="text-shadow: 0 1px 24px rgba(28,26,23,0.85);">Beyond Fragmented Learning.</h2>
        <div class="rule-gold mt-5"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="prose-editorial max-w-5xl mt-8">
        <p>In many professions, continuing education has become fragmented: isolated webinars, disconnected lectures, certificates without progression. Academia Europa was created to offer a more structured path: one that helps experienced professionals build mastery through carefully designed learning architecture, expert instruction, and disciplined academic standards.</p>
        <p>We are not a marketplace of courses. We are a European institution shaping a long-term ecosystem of professional education.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-3 right-4 text-[9px] text-white/40 select-none pointer-events-none">© Adobe Stock</div>
  </section>

  <!-- Featured Academy — VAI -->
  <Section eyebrow="First Academy" title="Veterinary Academy International." tone="ivory">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>Veterinary Academy International is the veterinary faculty of Academia Europa, dedicated to structured postgraduate education for veterinarians and veterinary teams. Evidence-based, accreditation-aligned, and built for professionals who demand more than fragmented CPD.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <a href="https://vai.vet" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">Visit VAI</a>
      <a href="/academies/vai" class="btn">Learn More</a>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-6 italic text-stone text-xs">Further specialist academies in development.</p>
  </Section>

  <!-- Light relief — The Academic Framework -->
  <section style="background-color: #F5F0E8; color: #2C2A27;">
    <div class="container-prose py-24 md:py-28">
      <div class="max-w-5xl">
        <div class="text-[0.75rem] uppercase font-medium mb-5" style="color: #8B6914; letter-spacing: 0.15em;">The Academic Framework</div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.1]" style="color: #2C2A27;">Standards and governance<br />are not a formality here.</h2>
        <p class="mt-10 max-w-[680px] text-lg leading-relaxed" style="color: #2C2A27;">
          Every programme developed under Academia Europa is built to a documented standard: defined learning objectives, structured module design, evidence-level distinctions, faculty documentation, assessment criteria, and scheduled review cycles. This is not compliance language. It is the foundation of educational integrity.
        </p>
        <hr class="border-0 h-px mt-14 mb-14" style="background-color: #C8B99A;" />
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 md:gap-12">
          <div>
            <div class="text-[0.7rem] uppercase font-medium mb-3" style="color: #8B6914; letter-spacing: 0.12em;">Learning Design</div>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-[15px]" style="color: #2C2A27;">Programmes are structured as complete learning systems, not collections of isolated content. Each module builds deliberately on the last.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-[0.7rem] uppercase font-medium mb-3" style="color: #8B6914; letter-spacing: 0.12em;">Evidence Standards</div>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-[15px]" style="color: #2C2A27;">Content is developed with defined evidence-level distinctions, from established clinical data to expert hypothesis, clearly labelled throughout.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-[0.7rem] uppercase font-medium mb-3" style="color: #8B6914; letter-spacing: 0.12em;">Review Cycles</div>
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-[15px]" style="color: #2C2A27;">All programmes carry a version date and undergo scheduled review to maintain currency, accuracy, and professional relevance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-14 text-center">
          <a href="/academic-standards" class="inline-block text-[0.8rem] uppercase transition-colors" style="color: #8B6914; letter-spacing: 0.12em;" onmouseover="this.style.color='#A07820'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#8B6914'">View Academic Standards →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Closing CTA — three audiences -->
  <section style="background-color: var(--color-charcoal-deep);">
    <div class="container-prose py-20 md:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-5xl">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-cream text-3xl md:text-5xl leading-tight">
          Academia Europa welcomes professionals, educators, and institutional partners.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-5 italic text-stone text-base">Three clear pathways into the institution.</p>
        <hr class="border-0 h-px my-12" style="background-color: #4A4743;" />
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 md:gap-12">
          <div>
            <div class="text-[0.7rem] uppercase font-medium mb-4 text-bronze" style="letter-spacing: 0.12em;">Professionals</div>
            <p class="text-cream-dim leading-relaxed text-[15px]">Structured programmes designed for practitioners seeking documented progression and genuine mastery in their field.</p>
            <a href="/academies" class="mt-5 inline-block text-[0.8rem] uppercase text-bronze hover:text-bronze-hover transition-colors" style="letter-spacing: 0.12em;">Explore Programmes →</a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-[0.7rem] uppercase font-medium mb-4 text-bronze" style="letter-spacing: 0.12em;">Faculty</div>
            <p class="text-cream-dim leading-relaxed text-[15px]">Teaching opportunities for specialists committed to rigorous, evidence-informed professional education within a structured academic framework.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="mt-5 inline-block text-[0.8rem] uppercase text-bronze hover:text-bronze-hover transition-colors" style="letter-spacing: 0.12em;">Join as Faculty →</a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-[0.7rem] uppercase font-medium mb-4 text-bronze" style="letter-spacing: 0.12em;">Institutions</div>
            <p class="text-cream-dim leading-relaxed text-[15px]">Academic review, co-development, and partnership frameworks for professional bodies aligned with our educational standards.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="mt-5 inline-block text-[0.8rem] uppercase text-bronze hover:text-bronze-hover transition-colors" style="letter-spacing: 0.12em;">Discuss Partnership →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr class="border-0 h-px my-12" style="background-color: #4A4743;" />
        <p class="text-center italic text-stone text-[11px]">All enquiries are handled by the academic office within five working days.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
